name: Forbidden island
description: Sunset on the Forbidden Island, one of the beautiful places to spend the evening in one of the Komodo National Park areas. squeezed by a beautiful beach and the island of bats which has thousands of bats that will come out when it gets dark. This is one of the memories part of my trip trying to surround Indonesia. and this is another part, when returning to NTB and NTT for 30 days in 2016.
